(firstQuint)Single Port Myomectomy Versus Conventional Myomectomy.

 There were several studies about feasibility and cosmetic benefit of single port laparoscopic adnexal surgery and hysterectomy compared to conventional multiport laparoscopic surgery.

 Meanwhile, no study mentioned benefit of single port laparoscopic surgery in myomectomy because single port myomectomy needs more labor and operator's skill than other pelvic surgery.

 At this point, the investigators need to verify the effectiveness and benefit of single port laparoscopic myomectomy.

